

start jenkins 

sudo systemctl start jenkins
sudo systemctl status jenkins
sudo ufw allow 8080
sudo ufw status
--->if not active<-----
sudo ufw allow OpenSSH
sudo ufw enable
http://localhost:8080/


- Run Jenkins in Docker
	- Run jenkins as a docker container from the jenkins/jenkins Docker image.
	
	- Run jenkins in docker : https://www.jenkins.io/doc/tutorials/build-a-python-app-with-pyinstaller/#on-macos-and-linux
	
	- Create a bridge network in Docker using the following " doker network create command" 
	


